## Bug Fix: AI模型配置菜单打开报错

### Root Cause

前端 AI 模型配置页面（`admin-web/src/app/(admin)/ai-config/page.tsx`）与后端 API 存在严重的契约不一致：
1. 后端 `GET /api/admin/ai-config` 返回 `{"items": [...]}`（列表），前端把响应当作单个配置对象使用
2. 前端使用 `baseUrl`/`model`/`apiKey` 等 camelCase 字段名，后端使用 `base_url`/`model_name`/`api_key` 等 snake_case
3. `currentConfig.apiKey.substring(0, 8)` 在 `apiKey` 为 `undefined` 时抛出 `TypeError`，导致客户端崩溃

### Backend

- Added `max_tokens` (Integer, default 4096) and `temperature` (Float, default 0.7) columns to `AIModelConfig` model (`backend/app/models/models.py`)
- Updated `AIModelConfigCreate`/`AIModelConfigUpdate`/`AIModelConfigResponse` schemas (`backend/app/schemas/admin.py`) to include `max_tokens`, `temperature`, and `api_key` fields
- Rewrote AI config API endpoints (`backend/app/api/admin.py`) — replaced `response_model` + Pydantic `model_validate()` with manual `_ai_config_to_dict()` helper to ensure all fields (including `max_tokens`, `temperature`, masked `api_key`) are always present in responses
- Added `_mask_api_key()` helper for API key display masking
- Added `_sync_ai_model_configs()` in `backend/app/services/schema_sync.py` for database migration (ALTER TABLE to add new columns)
- Updated `backend/app/services/ai_service.py` — `_get_active_model_config()` now returns `max_tokens`/`temperature` from DB config; `call_ai_model()` uses these values instead of hardcoded defaults

### Admin Web

- Completely rewrote `admin-web/src/app/(admin)/ai-config/page.tsx` — changed from single-config form to full CRUD list management with Ant Design Table + Modal. Supports create, edit, delete, and test connection. All field names now match backend snake_case convention (`provider_name`, `base_url`, `model_name`, `api_key`, `max_tokens`, `temperature`, `is_active`). Added proper null safety for all data access.

### Deployment

- Updated `docker-compose.prod.yml` — all container names now use DEPLOY_ID prefix (`3b7b999d-e51c-4c0d-8f6e-baf90cd26857-{service}`)
- Updated `gateway-routes.conf` — proxy_pass targets use DEPLOY_ID-prefixed container names with `set $target` variable pattern

## Notes For Next Iteration

- Merchant identities are granted by admin only; new self-registered accounts still default to normal users.
- Old user and merchant accounts require admin-side manual merge before official cutover.
- If remote DB schema lags behind models, check startup schema synchronization and the new merchant-related tables first.
- SMS config can be managed from admin panel (系统管理 → 短信管理). DB config takes priority over env vars. If neither is set, SMS sending raises RuntimeError (HTTP 500 to frontend).
- To enable real SMS sending: either configure via admin panel or set `TENCENT_SMS_SECRET_ID` and `TENCENT_SMS_SECRET_KEY` environment variables.
